-- China's Sunac in talks to buy 30 pct of fellow developer Greentown
-- By Clare Jim
-- Thu May 15, 2014 10:21PM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, May 16 (Reuters) - Sunac China Holdings Limited <1918.HK> said it is in talks to buy 30 percent of fellow property developer Greentown China Holding Ltd <3900.HK>, sending shares in Greentown 5 percent higher.    Greentown said that while the two companies were in discussions, it had not yet received a formal offer.

Sunac shares were down 7 percent as of 0157 GMT.